01 BACKGROUND

About Me

Building Better Systems

I'm a software engineer and solution architect with extensive experience building enterprise systems and supply chain applications. I specialize in database engineering, DevOps automation, and modernizing legacy systems at scale.

At Texas Instruments, I've invented and architected critical systems that improved developer productivity, optimized supply chain operations, and delivered measurable business impact. My work spans from automated version control systems to performance engineering for factory planning engines.

I'm passionate about solving complex technical challenges, mentoring teams, and creating solutions that make systems more reliable, maintainable, and efficient. My approach combines deep technical expertise with a focus on practical business outcomes.
